        "ult": "Super Mega Death Rocket!: fires a huge shark rocket across the map. On champion hit it explodes, deals heavy physical damage, and triggers Get Excited movement and attack speed."
      },
      "test_mod_jinx": {
        "name": "Jinx (Loose Cannon)",
        "attack": "Pow-Pow / Fishbones: basic attacks default to Pow-Pow and build minigun attack speed. During the short Fishbones window, attacks become splash rockets and clear Pow-Pow stacks.",
        "skill": "Switcheroo!: when an enemy target is available, Jinx briefly swaps to Fishbones for splash rocket attacks, then automatically returns to Pow-Pow.",
        "skill2": "Zap! + Flame Chompers!: fires a long electric shot that damages and slows, then throws Flame Chompers ahead to bite, stun, and burn enemies caught in the line.",
        "ult": "Super Mega Death Rocket!: fires a huge shark rocket across the map. On champion hit it explodes, deals heavy physical damage, and triggers Get Excited movement and attack speed."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_thresh": {
        "name": "Thresh (Chain Warden)",
        "attack": "Damnation / Flay chain: Thresh lashes with his chain scythe for <#ff9028ff>physical damage<> and a small <#a974ffff>magic burn<>. Every third basic attack becomes an empowered soul lash that slows the target and resets the chain-charge cycle.",
        "skill": "Q - Death Sentence: Thresh throws a non-piercing hook chain in a long line. The first enemy hit takes <#a974ffff>65<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> magic damage, is stunned, heavily slowed, and has movement skills briefly blocked. Champion hits grant a permanent Damnation soul stack.",
        "skill2": "W/E - Dark Passage / Flay: Thresh lights his lantern to shield himself, then sweeps the chain scythe forward. Enemies hit take magic damage, are pushed back, slowed, and grant a Damnation soul stack on champion hit.",
        "ult": "R - The Box: Thresh summons spectral prison walls around himself. Enemies inside take heavy magic damage, are strongly slowed, and have movement skills briefly blocked. The Box lingers as a slowing field, and champion hits grant permanent souls."
      },
      "test_mod_thresh": {
        "name": "Thresh (Chain Warden)",
        "attack": "Damnation / Flay chain: Thresh lashes with his chain scythe for <#ff9028ff>physical damage<> and a small <#a974ffff>magic burn<>. Every third basic attack becomes an empowered soul lash that slows the target and resets the chain-charge cycle.",
        "skill": "Q - Death Sentence: Thresh throws a non-piercing hook chain in a long line. The first enemy hit takes <#a974ffff>65<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> magic damage, is stunned, heavily slowed, and has movement skills briefly blocked. Champion hits grant a permanent Damnation soul stack.",
        "skill2": "W/E - Dark Passage / Flay: Thresh lights his lantern to shield himself, then sweeps the chain scythe forward. Enemies hit take magic damage, are pushed back, slowed, and grant a Damnation soul stack on champion hit.",
        "ult": "R - The Box: Thresh summons spectral prison walls around himself. Enemies inside take heavy magic damage, are strongly slowed, and have movement skills briefly blocked. The Box lingers as a slowing field, and champion hits grant permanent souls."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_darius": {
        "name": "Darius",
        "attack": "Hemorrhage: Darius, the Hand of Noxus, cleaves with his axe for <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% attack damage<> as physical damage and advances Hemorrhage. At five stacks he gains Noxian Might. If Crippling Strike is primed, the next attack deals heavier damage and <#ef5350ff>slows<> the target.",
        "skill": "Q - Decimate: Darius spins his axe in a red outer circle, dealing <#ff9028ff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>95% attack damage<> as physical damage, applying Hemorrhage, and healing himself when enemies are struck. During Noxian Might, Decimate deals more damage and heals more.",
        "skill2": "E/W - Apprehend and Crippling Strike: Darius sweeps his axe forward in a chain-like hook line, dealing <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>60% attack damage<>, briefly stunning, slowing, and blocking movement skills. The cast primes his next attack as Crippling Strike.",
        "ult": "R - Noxian Guillotine: Darius rushes behind an enemy champion and executes with true damage. The blow scales with Hemorrhage stacks, reaches its highest damage at five stacks or during Noxian Might, and plays Darius's Noxian Guillotine voice line."
      },
      "test_mod_darius": {
        "name": "Darius",
        "attack": "Hemorrhage: Darius, the Hand of Noxus, cleaves with his axe for <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% attack damage<> as physical damage and advances Hemorrhage. At five stacks he gains Noxian Might. If Crippling Strike is primed, the next attack deals heavier damage and <#ef5350ff>slows<> the target.",
        "skill": "Q - Decimate: Darius spins his axe in a red outer circle, dealing <#ff9028ff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>95% attack damage<> as physical damage, applying Hemorrhage, and healing himself when enemies are struck. During Noxian Might, Decimate deals more damage and heals more.",
        "skill2": "E/W - Apprehend and Crippling Strike: Darius sweeps his axe forward in a chain-like hook line, dealing <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>60% attack damage<>, briefly stunning, slowing, and blocking movement skills. The cast primes his next attack as Crippling Strike.",
        "ult": "R - Noxian Guillotine: Darius rushes behind an enemy champion and executes with true damage. The blow scales with Hemorrhage stacks, reaches its highest damage at five stacks or during Noxian Might, and plays Darius's Noxian Guillotine voice line."
      }
    }
  },
  "pt-BR": {
    "description": {
      "bo_league_champions_aatrox": {
        "name": "Aatrox",
        "attack": "Deathbringer Stance: empowers the next greatsword strike, dealing <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>112% attack damage<> as <#ff9028ff>physical damage<>.",
        "skill": "Q - The Darkin Blade: each cast releases one strike of Aatrox's three-part blade combo. Q1 is a narrow thrust, Q2 is a wide cleave, and Q3 is a heavy smash that hits hardest and <#ef5350ff>knocks enemies airborne for 0.5s<>. Casting Q again advances to the next strike instead of firing all three at once.",
        "skill2": "W - Infernal Chains: Aatrox fires a demonic chain in a line, damaging and <#ffb900ff>slowing<> enemy champions hit. After a short delay the chain snaps back, dealing damage again and briefly locking enemies caught in the path.",
        "ult": "R - World Ender: Aatrox reveals his demonic form for <#ffb900ff>10.0s<>, gaining <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>75 attack damage<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:speed_0><#ffffffff>20% movement speed<> and <#6aff55ff>50% vamp<>. Nearby enemies are briefly feared on cast."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_viktor": {
        "name": "Viktor",
        "attack": "Arcane Pulse: Viktor fires an arcane bolt, dealing <#a974ffff>12<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> as magic damage. While Siphon Empower is active, his next basic attack deals <#a974ffff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>115% magic power<> and grants Viktor a shield.",
        "skill": "E - Hextech Ray: Viktor's third arm fires a laser in the target direction, dealing magic damage to enemies in a line. When evolved, the ray leaves an aftershock that detonates shortly after, damaging and briefly slowing enemies. Hitting an enemy champion advances Glorious Evolution.",
        "skill2": "Q/W - Siphon Power + Gravity Field: Viktor shields himself and empowers his next basic attack, then creates a gravity field at the target location. Enemies inside are slowed; enemies still in the field when it collapses are stunned. When evolved, the field also disrupts movement skills.",
        "ult": "R - Arcane Storm: Viktor summons an arcane storm at the target location, dealing an initial burst of magic damage and disrupting enemy skills. The storm then pulses repeatedly. Casting Arcane Storm advances Glorious Evolution; once fully evolved, the storm is larger, lasts longer, and pulses faster."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_veigar": {
        "name": "Veigar",
        "attack": "Dispara um projétil mágico contra um alvo, causando <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% do dano de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>dano físico<>.",
        "skill": "Invoca matéria escura em um local-alvo após um curto atraso, causando <#a974ffff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>180% de AP<> de <#a974ffff>dano mágico<> em <#ffb900ff>35 de alcance<>. Acertos em campeões inimigos concedem <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>22 de AP até a morte<>; tropas sofrem metade do dano.",
        "skill2": "Cria uma jaula de Horizonte de Eventos. Após <#ffb900ff>1.0s<>, campeões inimigos dentro dela ficam <#ef5350ff>atordoados por 1.5s<> e a jaula desaparece.",
        "ult": "Dispara uma explosão de magia sombria contra um campeão inimigo, causando <#a974ffff>150<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>200% de AP<> de <#a974ffff>dano mágico<>."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_jhin": {
        "name": "Jhin",
        "attack": "Dispara um tiro contra o alvo, causando <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% do dano de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>dano físico<>. A cada quarto ataque, usa um projétil vermelho e causa <#ff9028ff>100<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>200% do dano de ataque<>. Após o quarto tiro, Jhin recarrega com velocidade de ataque muito reduzida até seu próximo ataque.",
        "skill": "Granada Dançante: arremessa uma granada saltitante em um inimigo dentro do alcance. A granada pode saltar para outro inimigo próximo e causa <#ff9028ff>40<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>75% do dano de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>dano físico<> ao atingir.",
        "skill2": "Florescer Mortal: dispara um tiro longo em linha reta, causando <#ff9028ff>70<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>70% do dano de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>dano físico<> a campeões inimigos e <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>30% do dano de ataque<> a tropas. Campeões inimigos atingidos ficam <#ef5350ff>atordoados por 0.5s<>.",
        "ult": "Aclamação: enraíza Jhin no lugar e dispara quatro projéteis que atingem apenas campeões na direção escolhida. Cada projétil para no primeiro campeão inimigo atingido. Os três primeiros tiros causam <#ff9028ff>300<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>150% do dano de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>dano físico<>; o quarto tiro vermelho, maior, causa <#ff9028ff>300<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>300% do dano de ataque<>."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_vayne": {
        "name": "Vayne",
        "attack": "Dispara um virote de besta contra o alvo, causando <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% do dano de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>dano físico<>. A cada terceiro ataque básico, ativa Dardos de Prata, causando <#f5f5f5ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>35% do dano de ataque<> + <#f5f5f5ff>4% da Vida máxima do alvo<> como <#f5f5f5ff>dano fixo<>.",
        "skill": "Rolamento: rola uma curta distância na direção escolhida e fortalece o próximo ataque básico para causar <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>150% do dano de ataque<>. Durante Hora Final, Rolamento percorre uma distância maior e deixa Vayne <#ffb900ff>invisível por 1.5s<>.",
        "skill2": "Dardos de Prata: passiva, disponível no nível 1 e sempre ativa. A cada terceiro ataque básico, causa <#f5f5f5ff>dano fixo<> adicional.",
        "ult": "Hora Final: por <#ffb900ff>10.0s<>, Vayne recebe <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>50 de dano de ataque<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:speed_0><#ffffffff>20% de velocidade de movimento<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:attack_speed_0><#ceff99ff>20% de velocidade de ataque<> e recuperação de habilidades mais rápida. Enquanto ativa, Rolamento concede invisibilidade."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_fiddlesticks": {
        "name": "Fiddlesticks",
        "attack": "Arremessa um projétil em forma de corvo contra o alvo, causando <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>dano mágico<>.",
        "skill": "Aterrorizar: envia um projétil de pesadelo contra um campeão inimigo, causando <#a974ffff>45<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>70% de AP<> de <#a974ffff>dano mágico<> e amedrontando-o por 1.25 segundos.",
        "skill2": "Colheita Farta: drena brevemente inimigos próximos, causando repetidamente <#a974ffff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>25% de AP<> de <#a974ffff>dano mágico<> e curando Fiddlesticks em <#6aff55ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#6aff55ff>8% de AP<> por inimigo atingido.",
        "ult": "Tempestade de Corvos: desloca-se instantaneamente até um campeão inimigo, amedronta brevemente campeões inimigos próximos e envolve Fiddlesticks em uma tempestade por 2 segundos, causando repetidamente <#a974ffff>26<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>30% de AP<> de <#a974ffff>dano mágico<> a inimigos próximos."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_azir": {
        "name": "Azir",
        "attack": "Azir comanda magia de areia contra o alvo, causando 75% de AP como dano mágico e ocasionalmente invocando soldados de areia para entrar na luta.",
        "skill": "Surja!: envia um soldado de areia a um local-alvo, causando 30 + 60% de AP como dano mágico aos inimigos atravessados. Ao chegar, o soldado permanece e ataca inimigos próximos, causando 15 + 70% de AP como dano mágico por golpe contra campeões.",
        "skill2": "Areias Oscilantes: invoca um soldado de areia e avança até ele, recebendo um escudo de 70 + 45% de AP. Inimigos atravessados por Azir sofrem 40 + 45% de AP como dano mágico. O soldado permanece após o avanço.",
        "ult": "Decreto do Imperador: envia uma parede de soldados para a frente, causando 120 + 100% de AP como dano mágico aos inimigos em seu caminho, empurrando-os para trás e arremessando-os brevemente ao ar. A parede permanece por pouco tempo, atrapalhando o movimento através dela."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_fizz": {
        "name": "Fizz",
        "attack": "Golpeia o alvo corpo a corpo, causando <#a974ffff>10<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>100% de AP<> de <#a974ffff>dano mágico<>. Após Ataque do Ouriço, ataques básicos aplicam veneno brevemente ao atingir.",
        "skill": "Ataque do Ouriço: avança através do alvo e aterrissa atrás dele, causando <#a974ffff>40<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>55% de AP<> de <#a974ffff>dano mágico<> e envenenando-o por <#ffb900ff>3.0s<>. Por <#ffb900ff>4.0s<> após atingir, os ataques básicos de Fizz aplicam um veneno mais fraco ao acertar.",
        "skill2": "Brincalhão / Trapaceiro: salta na direção de um inimigo ou aliado escolhido, pausa brevemente sobre o tridente enquanto fica <#ffb900ff>invisível, com dano reduzido e imune a controle de grupo por 2.4s<>, depois faz uma curta descida e cai causando <#a974ffff>70<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>65% de AP<> de <#a974ffff>dano mágico<> e <#ef5350ff>lentidão em inimigos próximos por 0.5s<>.",
        "ult": "Lançar Isca: arremessa um peixe de longo alcance na direção escolhida. O peixe para no primeiro campeão inimigo atingido, <#ef5350ff>aplicando forte lentidão por 2.5s<>; se errar, chega ao fim do percurso. Um tubarão aparece durante a lentidão e então emerge para causar <#a974ffff>240<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>140% de AP<> de <#a974ffff>dano mágico<> e <#ef5350ff>arremessar inimigos ao ar<>."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_ezreal": {
        "name": "Ezreal",
        "attack": "Dispara um projétil de energia contra o alvo, causando <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% do dano de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>dano físico<>.",
        "skill": "Disparo Místico: dispara um tiro de precisão rápido na direção escolhida, parando no primeiro inimigo atingido e causando <#ff9028ff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% do dano de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>dano físico<> a campeões. Tropas sofrem metade do dano.",
        "skill2": "Fluxo Arcano: teleporta-se por uma curta distância na direção escolhida.",
        "ult": "Barragem Incendiária: dispara um ataque de alcance ilimitado na direção dos inimigos, causando <#ff9028ff>220<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% do dano de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>dano físico<>, mais <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>70% AP<> como <#a974ffff>dano mágico<> aos inimigos atingidos."
      },
      "test_mod_aatrox": {
        "name": "Aatrox",
        "attack": "Deathbringer Stance: empowers the next greatsword strike, dealing <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>112% attack damage<> as <#ff9028ff>physical damage<>.",
        "skill": "Q - The Darkin Blade: each cast releases one strike of Aatrox's three-part blade combo. Q1 is a narrow thrust, Q2 is a wide cleave, and Q3 is a heavy smash that hits hardest and <#ef5350ff>knocks enemies airborne for 0.5s<>. Casting Q again advances to the next strike instead of firing all three at once.",
        "skill2": "W - Infernal Chains: Aatrox fires a demonic chain in a line, damaging and <#ffb900ff>slowing<> enemy champions hit. After a short delay the chain snaps back, dealing damage again and briefly locking enemies caught in the path.",
        "ult": "R - World Ender: Aatrox reveals his demonic form for <#ffb900ff>10.0s<>, gaining <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>75 attack damage<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:speed_0><#ffffffff>20% movement speed<> and <#6aff55ff>50% vamp<>. Nearby enemies are briefly feared on cast."
      },
      "test_mod_viktor": {
        "name": "Viktor",
        "attack": "Arcane Pulse: Viktor fires an arcane bolt, dealing <#a974ffff>12<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> as magic damage. While Siphon Empower is active, his next basic attack deals <#a974ffff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>115% magic power<> and grants Viktor a shield.",
        "skill": "E - Hextech Ray: Viktor's third arm fires a laser in the target direction, dealing magic damage to enemies in a line. When evolved, the ray leaves an aftershock that detonates shortly after, damaging and briefly slowing enemies. Hitting an enemy champion advances Glorious Evolution.",
        "skill2": "Q/W - Siphon Power + Gravity Field: Viktor shields himself and empowers his next basic attack, then creates a gravity field at the target location. Enemies inside are slowed; enemies still in the field when it collapses are stunned. When evolved, the field also disrupts movement skills.",
        "ult": "R - Arcane Storm: Viktor summons an arcane storm at the target location, dealing an initial burst of magic damage and disrupting enemy skills. The storm then pulses repeatedly. Casting Arcane Storm advances Glorious Evolution; once fully evolved, the storm is larger, lasts longer, and pulses faster."
      },
      "test_mod_veigar": {
