        "skill": "Q - Steel Tempest: each cast thrusts a wind blade forward, dealing <#ff9028ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>70% attack damage<>. The second Q is stronger. The third Q fires a tornado that knocks enemies airborne and readies Last Breath.",
        "skill2": "W/E - Sweeping Blade + Wind Wall: Yasuo dashes through the chosen direction, slicing enemies for <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>55% attack damage<>, gaining a small shield, then raises a wind wall that blocks movement skills and pushes enemies back.",
        "ult": "R - Last Breath: Yasuo blinks behind an enemy champion and strikes for <#ff9028ff>110<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>120% attack damage<>. If Steel Tempest tornado recently hit, Last Breath becomes empowered, dealing higher damage in an area and knocking enemies airborne."
      },
      "test_mod_yasuo": {
        "name": "Yasuo (Unforgiven)",
        "attack": "Way of the Wanderer: Yasuo slashes with his katana, dealing <#ff9028ff>8<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% attack damage<> physical damage. Every third basic attack grants a short Flow shield.",
        "skill": "Q - Steel Tempest: each cast thrusts a wind blade forward, dealing <#ff9028ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>70% attack damage<>. The second Q is stronger. The third Q fires a tornado that knocks enemies airborne and readies Last Breath.",
        "skill2": "W/E - Sweeping Blade + Wind Wall: Yasuo dashes through the chosen direction, slicing enemies for <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>55% attack damage<>, gaining a small shield, then raises a wind wall that blocks movement skills and pushes enemies back.",
        "ult": "R - Last Breath: Yasuo blinks behind an enemy champion and strikes for <#ff9028ff>110<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>120% attack damage<>. If Steel Tempest tornado recently hit, Last Breath becomes empowered, dealing higher damage in an area and knocking enemies airborne."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_jinx": {
        "name": "Jinx (Loose Cannon)",
        "attack": "Pow-Pow / Fishbones: basic attacks default to Pow-Pow and build minigun attack speed. During the short Fishbones window, attacks become splash rockets and clear Pow-Pow stacks.",
        "skill": "Switcheroo!: when an enemy target is available, Jinx briefly swaps to Fishbones for splash rocket attacks, then automatically returns to Pow-Pow.",
        "skill2": "Zap! + Flame Chompers!: fires a long electric shot that damages and slows, then throws Flame Chompers ahead to bite, stun, and burn enemies caught in the line.",
        "ult": "Super Mega Death Rocket!: fires a huge shark rocket across the map. On champion hit it explodes, deals heavy physical damage, and triggers Get Excited movement and attack speed."
      },
      "test_mod_jinx": {
        "name": "Jinx (Loose Cannon)",
        "attack": "Pow-Pow / Fishbones: basic attacks default to Pow-Pow and build minigun attack speed. During the short Fishbones window, attacks become splash rockets and clear Pow-Pow stacks.",
        "skill": "Switcheroo!: when an enemy target is available, Jinx briefly swaps to Fishbones for splash rocket attacks, then automatically returns to Pow-Pow.",
        "skill2": "Zap! + Flame Chompers!: fires a long electric shot that damages and slows, then throws Flame Chompers ahead to bite, stun, and burn enemies caught in the line.",
        "ult": "Super Mega Death Rocket!: fires a huge shark rocket across the map. On champion hit it explodes, deals heavy physical damage, and triggers Get Excited movement and attack speed."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_thresh": {
        "name": "Thresh (Chain Warden)",
        "attack": "Damnation / Flay chain: Thresh lashes with his chain scythe for <#ff9028ff>physical damage<> and a small <#a974ffff>magic burn<>. Every third basic attack becomes an empowered soul lash that slows the target and resets the chain-charge cycle.",
        "skill": "Q - Death Sentence: Thresh throws a non-piercing hook chain in a long line. The first enemy hit takes <#a974ffff>65<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> magic damage, is stunned, heavily slowed, and has movement skills briefly blocked. Champion hits grant a permanent Damnation soul stack.",
        "skill2": "W/E - Dark Passage / Flay: Thresh lights his lantern to shield himself, then sweeps the chain scythe forward. Enemies hit take magic damage, are pushed back, slowed, and grant a Damnation soul stack on champion hit.",
        "ult": "R - The Box: Thresh summons spectral prison walls around himself. Enemies inside take heavy magic damage, are strongly slowed, and have movement skills briefly blocked. The Box lingers as a slowing field, and champion hits grant permanent souls."
      },
      "test_mod_thresh": {
        "name": "Thresh (Chain Warden)",
        "attack": "Damnation / Flay chain: Thresh lashes with his chain scythe for <#ff9028ff>physical damage<> and a small <#a974ffff>magic burn<>. Every third basic attack becomes an empowered soul lash that slows the target and resets the chain-charge cycle.",
        "skill": "Q - Death Sentence: Thresh throws a non-piercing hook chain in a long line. The first enemy hit takes <#a974ffff>65<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> magic damage, is stunned, heavily slowed, and has movement skills briefly blocked. Champion hits grant a permanent Damnation soul stack.",
        "skill2": "W/E - Dark Passage / Flay: Thresh lights his lantern to shield himself, then sweeps the chain scythe forward. Enemies hit take magic damage, are pushed back, slowed, and grant a Damnation soul stack on champion hit.",
        "ult": "R - The Box: Thresh summons spectral prison walls around himself. Enemies inside take heavy magic damage, are strongly slowed, and have movement skills briefly blocked. The Box lingers as a slowing field, and champion hits grant permanent souls."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_darius": {
        "name": "Darius",
        "attack": "Hemorrhage: Darius, the Hand of Noxus, cleaves with his axe for <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% attack damage<> as physical damage and advances Hemorrhage. At five stacks he gains Noxian Might. If Crippling Strike is primed, the next attack deals heavier damage and <#ef5350ff>slows<> the target.",
        "skill": "Q - Decimate: Darius spins his axe in a red outer circle, dealing <#ff9028ff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>95% attack damage<> as physical damage, applying Hemorrhage, and healing himself when enemies are struck. During Noxian Might, Decimate deals more damage and heals more.",
        "skill2": "E/W - Apprehend and Crippling Strike: Darius sweeps his axe forward in a chain-like hook line, dealing <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>60% attack damage<>, briefly stunning, slowing, and blocking movement skills. The cast primes his next attack as Crippling Strike.",
        "ult": "R - Noxian Guillotine: Darius rushes behind an enemy champion and executes with true damage. The blow scales with Hemorrhage stacks, reaches its highest damage at five stacks or during Noxian Might, and plays Darius's Noxian Guillotine voice line."
      },
      "test_mod_darius": {
        "name": "Darius",
        "attack": "Hemorrhage: Darius, the Hand of Noxus, cleaves with his axe for <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% attack damage<> as physical damage and advances Hemorrhage. At five stacks he gains Noxian Might. If Crippling Strike is primed, the next attack deals heavier damage and <#ef5350ff>slows<> the target.",
        "skill": "Q - Decimate: Darius spins his axe in a red outer circle, dealing <#ff9028ff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>95% attack damage<> as physical damage, applying Hemorrhage, and healing himself when enemies are struck. During Noxian Might, Decimate deals more damage and heals more.",
        "skill2": "E/W - Apprehend and Crippling Strike: Darius sweeps his axe forward in a chain-like hook line, dealing <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>60% attack damage<>, briefly stunning, slowing, and blocking movement skills. The cast primes his next attack as Crippling Strike.",
        "ult": "R - Noxian Guillotine: Darius rushes behind an enemy champion and executes with true damage. The blow scales with Hemorrhage stacks, reaches its highest damage at five stacks or during Noxian Might, and plays Darius's Noxian Guillotine voice line."
      }
    }
  },
  "es-ES": {
    "description": {
      "bo_league_champions_aatrox": {
        "name": "Aatrox",
        "attack": "Deathbringer Stance: empowers the next greatsword strike, dealing <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>112% attack damage<> as <#ff9028ff>physical damage<>.",
        "skill": "Q - The Darkin Blade: each cast releases one strike of Aatrox's three-part blade combo. Q1 is a narrow thrust, Q2 is a wide cleave, and Q3 is a heavy smash that hits hardest and <#ef5350ff>knocks enemies airborne for 0.5s<>. Casting Q again advances to the next strike instead of firing all three at once.",
        "skill2": "W - Infernal Chains: Aatrox fires a demonic chain in a line, damaging and <#ffb900ff>slowing<> enemy champions hit. After a short delay the chain snaps back, dealing damage again and briefly locking enemies caught in the path.",
        "ult": "R - World Ender: Aatrox reveals his demonic form for <#ffb900ff>10.0s<>, gaining <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>75 attack damage<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:speed_0><#ffffffff>20% movement speed<> and <#6aff55ff>50% vamp<>. Nearby enemies are briefly feared on cast."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_viktor": {
        "name": "Viktor",
        "attack": "Arcane Pulse: Viktor fires an arcane bolt, dealing <#a974ffff>12<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> as magic damage. While Siphon Empower is active, his next basic attack deals <#a974ffff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>115% magic power<> and grants Viktor a shield.",
        "skill": "E - Hextech Ray: Viktor's third arm fires a laser in the target direction, dealing magic damage to enemies in a line. When evolved, the ray leaves an aftershock that detonates shortly after, damaging and briefly slowing enemies. Hitting an enemy champion advances Glorious Evolution.",
        "skill2": "Q/W - Siphon Power + Gravity Field: Viktor shields himself and empowers his next basic attack, then creates a gravity field at the target location. Enemies inside are slowed; enemies still in the field when it collapses are stunned. When evolved, the field also disrupts movement skills.",
        "ult": "R - Arcane Storm: Viktor summons an arcane storm at the target location, dealing an initial burst of magic damage and disrupting enemy skills. The storm then pulses repeatedly. Casting Arcane Storm advances Glorious Evolution; once fully evolved, the storm is larger, lasts longer, and pulses faster."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_veigar": {
        "name": "Veigar",
        "attack": "Dispara un proyectil mágico al objetivo e inflige <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>.",
        "skill": "Hace caer materia oscura en la ubicación objetivo tras un breve retraso, inflige <#a974ffff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>180% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> en <#ffb900ff>35 de alcance<>. Golpear campeones enemigos otorga <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>22 de AP hasta morir<>; los súbditos reciben la mitad de daño.",
        "skill2": "Crea una jaula de Horizonte de Sucesos. Tras <#ffb900ff>1.0 s<>, los campeones enemigos dentro quedan <#ef5350ff>aturdidos durante 1.5 s<> y la jaula desaparece.",
        "ult": "Dispara una ráfaga de magia oscura a un campeón enemigo e inflige <#a974ffff>150<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>200% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<>."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_jhin": {
        "name": "Jhin",
        "attack": "Dispara al objetivo e inflige <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>. Cada cuarto ataque usa un proyectil rojo e inflige <#ff9028ff>100<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>200% de daño de ataque<>. Tras el cuarto disparo, Jhin recarga con velocidad de ataque muy reducida hasta su siguiente ataque.",
        "skill": "Granada Danzante: lanza una granada que rebota a un enemigo dentro del alcance. La granada puede saltar a otro enemigo cercano e inflige <#ff9028ff>40<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>75% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<> al impactar.",
        "skill2": "Florecer Mortal: dispara una línea larga que inflige <#ff9028ff>70<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>70% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<> a campeones enemigos y <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>30% de daño de ataque<> a súbditos. Los campeones enemigos alcanzados quedan <#ef5350ff>aturdidos durante 0.5 s<>.",
        "ult": "Llamada del Telón: inmoviliza a Jhin y dispara cuatro balas que solo afectan a campeones en la dirección elegida. Cada bala se detiene en el primer campeón enemigo alcanzado. Los tres primeros disparos infligen <#ff9028ff>300<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>150% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>; el cuarto disparo rojo más grande inflige <#ff9028ff>300<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>300% de daño de ataque<>."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_vayne": {
        "name": "Vayne",
        "attack": "Dispara un virote de ballesta al objetivo e inflige <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>. Cada tercer ataque básico activa Proyectiles de Plata, inflige <#f5f5f5ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>35% de daño de ataque<> + <#f5f5f5ff>4% de la vida máxima del objetivo<> como <#f5f5f5ff>daño fijo<>.",
        "skill": "Voltereta: rueda una corta distancia en la dirección elegida y potencia el siguiente ataque básico para que inflija <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>150% de daño de ataque<>. Durante Hora Final, Voltereta llega más lejos y vuelve a Vayne <#ffb900ff>invisible durante 1.5 s<>.",
        "skill2": "Proyectiles de Plata: pasiva, disponible desde el nivel 1 y siempre activa. Cada tercer ataque básico inflige <#f5f5f5ff>daño fijo<> adicional.",
        "ult": "Hora Final: durante <#ffb900ff>10.0 s<>, Vayne obtiene <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>50 de daño de ataque<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:speed_0><#ffffffff>20% de velocidad de movimiento<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:attack_speed_0><#ceff99ff>20% de velocidad de ataque<> y recuperación de enfriamiento de habilidades más rápida. Mientras está activa, Voltereta otorga invisibilidad."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_fiddlesticks": {
        "name": "Fiddlesticks",
        "attack": "Lanza un proyectil con forma de cuervo al objetivo e inflige <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<>.",
        "skill": "Aterrorizar: envía un proyectil de pesadilla a un campeón enemigo, inflige <#a974ffff>45<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>70% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> y lo aterroriza durante 1.25 segundos.",
        "skill2": "Cosecha Abundante: drena brevemente a enemigos cercanos, inflige repetidamente <#a974ffff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>25% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> y cura a Fiddlesticks <#6aff55ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#6aff55ff>8% de AP<> por cada enemigo alcanzado.",
        "ult": "Tormenta de Cuervos: se teleporta a un campeón enemigo, aterroriza brevemente a los campeones enemigos cercanos y rodea a Fiddlesticks con una tormenta durante 2 segundos, infligiendo repetidamente <#a974ffff>26<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>30% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> a enemigos cercanos."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_azir": {
        "name": "Azir",
        "attack": "Azir ordena magia de arena contra el objetivo, inflige 75% de AP como daño mágico y ocasionalmente invoca soldados de arena para unirse al combate.",
        "skill": "¡Alzaos!: envía un soldado de arena a una ubicación objetivo, inflige 30 + 60% de AP como daño mágico a los enemigos que atraviesa. Al llegar, el soldado permanece y ataca a enemigos cercanos, infligiendo 15 + 70% de AP como daño mágico por golpe a campeones.",
        "skill2": "Arenas Movedizas: invoca un soldado de arena y se desliza hasta él, obteniendo un escudo de 70 + 45% de AP. Los enemigos atravesados por Azir reciben 40 + 45% de AP como daño mágico. El soldado permanece después del desplazamiento.",
        "ult": "Falange Imperial: envía un muro de soldados hacia delante, inflige 120 + 100% de AP como daño mágico a los enemigos en su trayectoria, los empuja hacia atrás y los lanza brevemente por los aires. El muro permanece brevemente y dificulta el movimiento a través de él."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_fizz": {
        "name": "Fizz",
        "attack": "Golpea al objetivo cuerpo a cuerpo e inflige <#a974ffff>10<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>100% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<>. Después de Golpe de Erizo, los ataques básicos aplican brevemente veneno al impactar.",
        "skill": "Golpe de Erizo: se desliza a través del objetivo y aterriza detrás de él, inflige <#a974ffff>40<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>55% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> y lo envenena durante <#ffb900ff>3.0 s<>. Durante <#ffb900ff>4.0 s<> tras acertar, los ataques básicos de Fizz aplican un veneno más débil al impactar.",
        "skill2": "Juguetón / Bromista: salta hacia una dirección elegida de enemigo o aliado, se detiene brevemente sobre el tridente mientras está <#ffb900ff>invisible, con daño reducido e inmune al control durante 2.4 s<>, luego desciende una corta distancia y cae salpicando para infligir <#a974ffff>70<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>65% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> y <#ef5350ff>ralentizar a enemigos cercanos durante 0.5 s<>.",
        "ult": "Carnada para Tiburones: lanza un pez de largo alcance en la dirección elegida. El pez se detiene en el primer campeón enemigo alcanzado y lo <#ef5350ff>ralentiza fuertemente durante 2.5 s<>; si falla, llega al final de su trayectoria. Un tiburón aparece durante la ralentización y luego emerge para infligir <#a974ffff>240<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>140% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> y <#ef5350ff>lanzar por los aires a los enemigos<>."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_ezreal": {
        "name": "Ezreal",
        "attack": "Dispara un proyectil de energía al objetivo e inflige <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>.",
        "skill": "Disparo Místico: dispara un tiro de habilidad rápido en la dirección elegida, se detiene en el primer enemigo alcanzado e inflige <#ff9028ff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<> a campeones. Los súbditos reciben la mitad de daño.",
        "skill2": "Alteración Arcana: parpadea una corta distancia en la dirección elegida.",
        "ult": "Andanada Certera: dispara un ataque de alcance ilimitado hacia los enemigos, inflige <#ff9028ff>220<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>, más <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>70% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> a los enemigos alcanzados."
      },
      "test_mod_aatrox": {
        "name": "Aatrox",
        "attack": "Deathbringer Stance: empowers the next greatsword strike, dealing <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>112% attack damage<> as <#ff9028ff>physical damage<>.",
        "skill": "Q - The Darkin Blade: each cast releases one strike of Aatrox's three-part blade combo. Q1 is a narrow thrust, Q2 is a wide cleave, and Q3 is a heavy smash that hits hardest and <#ef5350ff>knocks enemies airborne for 0.5s<>. Casting Q again advances to the next strike instead of firing all three at once.",
        "skill2": "W - Infernal Chains: Aatrox fires a demonic chain in a line, damaging and <#ffb900ff>slowing<> enemy champions hit. After a short delay the chain snaps back, dealing damage again and briefly locking enemies caught in the path.",
        "ult": "R - World Ender: Aatrox reveals his demonic form for <#ffb900ff>10.0s<>, gaining <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>75 attack damage<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:speed_0><#ffffffff>20% movement speed<> and <#6aff55ff>50% vamp<>. Nearby enemies are briefly feared on cast."
      },
      "test_mod_viktor": {
        "name": "Viktor",
        "attack": "Arcane Pulse: Viktor fires an arcane bolt, dealing <#a974ffff>12<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> as magic damage. While Siphon Empower is active, his next basic attack deals <#a974ffff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>115% magic power<> and grants Viktor a shield.",
        "skill": "E - Hextech Ray: Viktor's third arm fires a laser in the target direction, dealing magic damage to enemies in a line. When evolved, the ray leaves an aftershock that detonates shortly after, damaging and briefly slowing enemies. Hitting an enemy champion advances Glorious Evolution.",
        "skill2": "Q/W - Siphon Power + Gravity Field: Viktor shields himself and empowers his next basic attack, then creates a gravity field at the target location. Enemies inside are slowed; enemies still in the field when it collapses are stunned. When evolved, the field also disrupts movement skills.",
        "ult": "R - Arcane Storm: Viktor summons an arcane storm at the target location, dealing an initial burst of magic damage and disrupting enemy skills. The storm then pulses repeatedly. Casting Arcane Storm advances Glorious Evolution; once fully evolved, the storm is larger, lasts longer, and pulses faster."
      },
      "test_mod_veigar": {
        "name": "Veigar",
        "attack": "Dispara un proyectil mágico al objetivo e inflige <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>.",
        "skill": "Hace caer materia oscura en la ubicación objetivo tras un breve retraso, inflige <#a974ffff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>180% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> en <#ffb900ff>35 de alcance<>. Golpear campeones enemigos otorga <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>22 de AP hasta morir<>; los súbditos reciben la mitad de daño.",
        "skill2": "Crea una jaula de Horizonte de Sucesos. Tras <#ffb900ff>1.0 s<>, los campeones enemigos dentro quedan <#ef5350ff>aturdidos durante 1.5 s<> y la jaula desaparece.",
        "ult": "Dispara una ráfaga de magia oscura a un campeón enemigo e inflige <#a974ffff>150<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>200% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<>."
      },
      "test_mod_jhin": {
        "name": "Jhin",
        "attack": "Dispara al objetivo e inflige <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>. Cada cuarto ataque usa un proyectil rojo e inflige <#ff9028ff>100<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>200% de daño de ataque<>. Tras el cuarto disparo, Jhin recarga con velocidad de ataque muy reducida hasta su siguiente ataque.",
        "skill": "Granada Danzante: lanza una granada que rebota a un enemigo dentro del alcance. La granada puede saltar a otro enemigo cercano e inflige <#ff9028ff>40<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>75% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<> al impactar.",
        "skill2": "Florecer Mortal: dispara una línea larga que inflige <#ff9028ff>70<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>70% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<> a campeones enemigos y <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>30% de daño de ataque<> a súbditos. Los campeones enemigos alcanzados quedan <#ef5350ff>aturdidos durante 0.5 s<>.",
        "ult": "Llamada del Telón: inmoviliza a Jhin y dispara cuatro balas que solo afectan a campeones en la dirección elegida. Cada bala se detiene en el primer campeón enemigo alcanzado. Los tres primeros disparos infligen <#ff9028ff>300<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>150% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>; el cuarto disparo rojo más grande inflige <#ff9028ff>300<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>300% de daño de ataque<>."
      },
      "test_mod_vayne": {
        "name": "Vayne",
        "attack": "Dispara un virote de ballesta al objetivo e inflige <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>. Cada tercer ataque básico activa Proyectiles de Plata, inflige <#f5f5f5ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>35% de daño de ataque<> + <#f5f5f5ff>4% de la vida máxima del objetivo<> como <#f5f5f5ff>daño fijo<>.",
        "skill": "Voltereta: rueda una corta distancia en la dirección elegida y potencia el siguiente ataque básico para que inflija <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>150% de daño de ataque<>. Durante Hora Final, Voltereta llega más lejos y vuelve a Vayne <#ffb900ff>invisible durante 1.5 s<>.",
        "skill2": "Proyectiles de Plata: pasiva, disponible desde el nivel 1 y siempre activa. Cada tercer ataque básico inflige <#f5f5f5ff>daño fijo<> adicional.",
        "ult": "Hora Final: durante <#ffb900ff>10.0 s<>, Vayne obtiene <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>50 de daño de ataque<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:speed_0><#ffffffff>20% de velocidad de movimiento<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:attack_speed_0><#ceff99ff>20% de velocidad de ataque<> y recuperación de enfriamiento de habilidades más rápida. Mientras está activa, Voltereta otorga invisibilidad."
      },
      "test_mod_fiddlesticks": {
        "name": "Fiddlesticks",
        "attack": "Lanza un proyectil con forma de cuervo al objetivo e inflige <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<>.",
        "skill": "Aterrorizar: envía un proyectil de pesadilla a un campeón enemigo, inflige <#a974ffff>45<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>70% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> y lo aterroriza durante 1.25 segundos.",
        "skill2": "Cosecha Abundante: drena brevemente a enemigos cercanos, inflige repetidamente <#a974ffff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>25% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> y cura a Fiddlesticks <#6aff55ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#6aff55ff>8% de AP<> por cada enemigo alcanzado.",
        "ult": "Tormenta de Cuervos: se teleporta a un campeón enemigo, aterroriza brevemente a los campeones enemigos cercanos y rodea a Fiddlesticks con una tormenta durante 2 segundos, infligiendo repetidamente <#a974ffff>26<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>30% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> a enemigos cercanos."
      },
      "test_mod_azir": {
        "name": "Azir",
        "attack": "Azir ordena magia de arena contra el objetivo, inflige 75% de AP como daño mágico y ocasionalmente invoca soldados de arena para unirse al combate.",
        "skill": "¡Alzaos!: envía un soldado de arena a una ubicación objetivo, inflige 30 + 60% de AP como daño mágico a los enemigos que atraviesa. Al llegar, el soldado permanece y ataca a enemigos cercanos, infligiendo 15 + 70% de AP como daño mágico por golpe a campeones.",
        "skill2": "Arenas Movedizas: invoca un soldado de arena y se desliza hasta él, obteniendo un escudo de 70 + 45% de AP. Los enemigos atravesados por Azir reciben 40 + 45% de AP como daño mágico. El soldado permanece después del desplazamiento.",
        "ult": "Falange Imperial: envía un muro de soldados hacia delante, inflige 120 + 100% de AP como daño mágico a los enemigos en su trayectoria, los empuja hacia atrás y los lanza brevemente por los aires. El muro permanece brevemente y dificulta el movimiento a través de él."
      },
      "test_mod_fizz": {
        "name": "Fizz",
        "attack": "Golpea al objetivo cuerpo a cuerpo e inflige <#a974ffff>10<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>100% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<>. Después de Golpe de Erizo, los ataques básicos aplican brevemente veneno al impactar.",
        "skill": "Golpe de Erizo: se desliza a través del objetivo y aterriza detrás de él, inflige <#a974ffff>40<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>55% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> y lo envenena durante <#ffb900ff>3.0 s<>. Durante <#ffb900ff>4.0 s<> tras acertar, los ataques básicos de Fizz aplican un veneno más débil al impactar.",
        "skill2": "Juguetón / Bromista: salta hacia una dirección elegida de enemigo o aliado, se detiene brevemente sobre el tridente mientras está <#ffb900ff>invisible, con daño reducido e inmune al control durante 2.4 s<>, luego desciende una corta distancia y cae salpicando para infligir <#a974ffff>70<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>65% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> y <#ef5350ff>ralentizar a enemigos cercanos durante 0.5 s<>.",
        "ult": "Carnada para Tiburones: lanza un pez de largo alcance en la dirección elegida. El pez se detiene en el primer campeón enemigo alcanzado y lo <#ef5350ff>ralentiza fuertemente durante 2.5 s<>; si falla, llega al final de su trayectoria. Un tiburón aparece durante la ralentización y luego emerge para infligir <#a974ffff>240<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>140% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> y <#ef5350ff>lanzar por los aires a los enemigos<>."
      },
      "test_mod_ezreal": {
        "name": "Ezreal",
        "attack": "Dispara un proyectil de energía al objetivo e inflige <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>.",
        "skill": "Disparo Místico: dispara un tiro de habilidad rápido en la dirección elegida, se detiene en el primer enemigo alcanzado e inflige <#ff9028ff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<> a campeones. Los súbditos reciben la mitad de daño.",
        "skill2": "Alteración Arcana: parpadea una corta distancia en la dirección elegida.",
        "ult": "Andanada Certera: dispara un ataque de alcance ilimitado hacia los enemigos, inflige <#ff9028ff>220<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% de daño de ataque<> como <#ff9028ff>daño físico<>, más <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>70% de AP<> como <#a974ffff>daño mágico<> a los enemigos alcanzados."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_kayn": {
        "name": "Kayn (Shadow Reaper)",
        "attack": "Shadow Reaper - Darkin Scythe: Kayn sweeps with his scythe, dealing <#ff9028ff>10<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>105% attack damage<> as physical damage. While Darkin Ascension is active, the strike hits harder and heals Kayn.",
        "skill": "Q - Reaping Slash: Kayn dashes a short distance and slashes in front of him, dealing <#ff9028ff>45<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>85% attack damage<> physical damage. Darkin Ascension empowers the slash.",
        "skill2": "W - Blade's Reach: Kayn carves a long line with his scythe, dealing <#ff9028ff>70<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>95% attack damage<> physical damage and <#ffb900ff>slowing enemies for 1.0s<>. In Darkin Ascension it is wider and briefly knocks enemies airborne.",
        "ult": "R - Umbral Trespass: Kayn enters an enemy champion, becoming untargetable for a short moment, then bursts out to deal <#ff9028ff>180<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>160% attack damage<> physical damage and gains Darkin Ascension for <#ffb900ff>10.0s<>."
      },
      "test_mod_kayn": {
        "name": "Kayn (Shadow Reaper)",
        "attack": "Shadow Reaper - Darkin Scythe: Kayn sweeps with his scythe, dealing <#ff9028ff>10<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>105% attack damage<> as physical damage. While Darkin Ascension is active, the strike hits harder and heals Kayn.",
        "skill": "Q - Reaping Slash: Kayn dashes a short distance and slashes in front of him, dealing <#ff9028ff>45<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>85% attack damage<> physical damage. Darkin Ascension empowers the slash.",
        "skill2": "W - Blade's Reach: Kayn carves a long line with his scythe, dealing <#ff9028ff>70<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>95% attack damage<> physical damage and <#ffb900ff>slowing enemies for 1.0s<>. In Darkin Ascension it is wider and briefly knocks enemies airborne.",
        "ult": "R - Umbral Trespass: Kayn enters an enemy champion, becoming untargetable for a short moment, then bursts out to deal <#ff9028ff>180<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>160% attack damage<> physical damage and gains Darkin Ascension for <#ffb900ff>10.0s<>."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_yasuo": {
        "name": "Yasuo (Unforgiven)",
        "attack": "Way of the Wanderer: Yasuo slashes with his katana, dealing <#ff9028ff>8<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% attack damage<> physical damage. Every third basic attack grants a short Flow shield.",
        "skill": "Q - Steel Tempest: each cast thrusts a wind blade forward, dealing <#ff9028ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>70% attack damage<>. The second Q is stronger. The third Q fires a tornado that knocks enemies airborne and readies Last Breath.",
        "skill2": "W/E - Sweeping Blade + Wind Wall: Yasuo dashes through the chosen direction, slicing enemies for <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>55% attack damage<>, gaining a small shield, then raises a wind wall that blocks movement skills and pushes enemies back.",
        "ult": "R - Last Breath: Yasuo blinks behind an enemy champion and strikes for <#ff9028ff>110<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>120% attack damage<>. If Steel Tempest tornado recently hit, Last Breath becomes empowered, dealing higher damage in an area and knocking enemies airborne."
      },
      "test_mod_yasuo": {
        "name": "Yasuo (Unforgiven)",
        "attack": "Way of the Wanderer: Yasuo slashes with his katana, dealing <#ff9028ff>8<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% attack damage<> physical damage. Every third basic attack grants a short Flow shield.",
        "skill": "Q - Steel Tempest: each cast thrusts a wind blade forward, dealing <#ff9028ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>70% attack damage<>. The second Q is stronger. The third Q fires a tornado that knocks enemies airborne and readies Last Breath.",
        "skill2": "W/E - Sweeping Blade + Wind Wall: Yasuo dashes through the chosen direction, slicing enemies for <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>55% attack damage<>, gaining a small shield, then raises a wind wall that blocks movement skills and pushes enemies back.",
        "ult": "R - Last Breath: Yasuo blinks behind an enemy champion and strikes for <#ff9028ff>110<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>120% attack damage<>. If Steel Tempest tornado recently hit, Last Breath becomes empowered, dealing higher damage in an area and knocking enemies airborne."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_jinx": {
        "name": "Jinx (Loose Cannon)",
        "attack": "Pow-Pow / Fishbones: basic attacks default to Pow-Pow and build minigun attack speed. During the short Fishbones window, attacks become splash rockets and clear Pow-Pow stacks.",
        "skill": "Switcheroo!: when an enemy target is available, Jinx briefly swaps to Fishbones for splash rocket attacks, then automatically returns to Pow-Pow.",
        "skill2": "Zap! + Flame Chompers!: fires a long electric shot that damages and slows, then throws Flame Chompers ahead to bite, stun, and burn enemies caught in the line.",
        "ult": "Super Mega Death Rocket!: fires a huge shark rocket across the map. On champion hit it explodes, deals heavy physical damage, and triggers Get Excited movement and attack speed."
      },
      "test_mod_jinx": {
        "name": "Jinx (Loose Cannon)",
        "attack": "Pow-Pow / Fishbones: basic attacks default to Pow-Pow and build minigun attack speed. During the short Fishbones window, attacks become splash rockets and clear Pow-Pow stacks.",
        "skill": "Switcheroo!: when an enemy target is available, Jinx briefly swaps to Fishbones for splash rocket attacks, then automatically returns to Pow-Pow.",
        "skill2": "Zap! + Flame Chompers!: fires a long electric shot that damages and slows, then throws Flame Chompers ahead to bite, stun, and burn enemies caught in the line.",
        "ult": "Super Mega Death Rocket!: fires a huge shark rocket across the map. On champion hit it explodes, deals heavy physical damage, and triggers Get Excited movement and attack speed."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_thresh": {
        "name": "Thresh (Chain Warden)",
        "attack": "Damnation / Flay chain: Thresh lashes with his chain scythe for <#ff9028ff>physical damage<> and a small <#a974ffff>magic burn<>. Every third basic attack becomes an empowered soul lash that slows the target and resets the chain-charge cycle.",
        "skill": "Q - Death Sentence: Thresh throws a non-piercing hook chain in a long line. The first enemy hit takes <#a974ffff>65<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> magic damage, is stunned, heavily slowed, and has movement skills briefly blocked. Champion hits grant a permanent Damnation soul stack.",
        "skill2": "W/E - Dark Passage / Flay: Thresh lights his lantern to shield himself, then sweeps the chain scythe forward. Enemies hit take magic damage, are pushed back, slowed, and grant a Damnation soul stack on champion hit.",
        "ult": "R - The Box: Thresh summons spectral prison walls around himself. Enemies inside take heavy magic damage, are strongly slowed, and have movement skills briefly blocked. The Box lingers as a slowing field, and champion hits grant permanent souls."
      },
      "test_mod_thresh": {
        "name": "Thresh (Chain Warden)",
        "attack": "Damnation / Flay chain: Thresh lashes with his chain scythe for <#ff9028ff>physical damage<> and a small <#a974ffff>magic burn<>. Every third basic attack becomes an empowered soul lash that slows the target and resets the chain-charge cycle.",
        "skill": "Q - Death Sentence: Thresh throws a non-piercing hook chain in a long line. The first enemy hit takes <#a974ffff>65<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> magic damage, is stunned, heavily slowed, and has movement skills briefly blocked. Champion hits grant a permanent Damnation soul stack.",
        "skill2": "W/E - Dark Passage / Flay: Thresh lights his lantern to shield himself, then sweeps the chain scythe forward. Enemies hit take magic damage, are pushed back, slowed, and grant a Damnation soul stack on champion hit.",
        "ult": "R - The Box: Thresh summons spectral prison walls around himself. Enemies inside take heavy magic damage, are strongly slowed, and have movement skills briefly blocked. The Box lingers as a slowing field, and champion hits grant permanent souls."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_darius": {
        "name": "Darius",
        "attack": "Hemorrhage: Darius, the Hand of Noxus, cleaves with his axe for <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% attack damage<> as physical damage and advances Hemorrhage. At five stacks he gains Noxian Might. If Crippling Strike is primed, the next attack deals heavier damage and <#ef5350ff>slows<> the target.",
        "skill": "Q - Decimate: Darius spins his axe in a red outer circle, dealing <#ff9028ff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>95% attack damage<> as physical damage, applying Hemorrhage, and healing himself when enemies are struck. During Noxian Might, Decimate deals more damage and heals more.",
        "skill2": "E/W - Apprehend and Crippling Strike: Darius sweeps his axe forward in a chain-like hook line, dealing <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>60% attack damage<>, briefly stunning, slowing, and blocking movement skills. The cast primes his next attack as Crippling Strike.",
        "ult": "R - Noxian Guillotine: Darius rushes behind an enemy champion and executes with true damage. The blow scales with Hemorrhage stacks, reaches its highest damage at five stacks or during Noxian Might, and plays Darius's Noxian Guillotine voice line."
      },
      "test_mod_darius": {
        "name": "Darius",
        "attack": "Hemorrhage: Darius, the Hand of Noxus, cleaves with his axe for <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% attack damage<> as physical damage and advances Hemorrhage. At five stacks he gains Noxian Might. If Crippling Strike is primed, the next attack deals heavier damage and <#ef5350ff>slows<> the target.",
        "skill": "Q - Decimate: Darius spins his axe in a red outer circle, dealing <#ff9028ff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>95% attack damage<> as physical damage, applying Hemorrhage, and healing himself when enemies are struck. During Noxian Might, Decimate deals more damage and heals more.",
        "skill2": "E/W - Apprehend and Crippling Strike: Darius sweeps his axe forward in a chain-like hook line, dealing <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>60% attack damage<>, briefly stunning, slowing, and blocking movement skills. The cast primes his next attack as Crippling Strike.",
        "ult": "R - Noxian Guillotine: Darius rushes behind an enemy champion and executes with true damage. The blow scales with Hemorrhage stacks, reaches its highest damage at five stacks or during Noxian Might, and plays Darius's Noxian Guillotine voice line."
      }
    }
  },
  "fr": {
    "description": {
      "bo_league_champions_aatrox": {
        "name": "Aatrox",
        "attack": "Deathbringer Stance: empowers the next greatsword strike, dealing <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>112% attack damage<> as <#ff9028ff>physical damage<>.",
        "skill": "Q - The Darkin Blade: each cast releases one strike of Aatrox's three-part blade combo. Q1 is a narrow thrust, Q2 is a wide cleave, and Q3 is a heavy smash that hits hardest and <#ef5350ff>knocks enemies airborne for 0.5s<>. Casting Q again advances to the next strike instead of firing all three at once.",
        "skill2": "W - Infernal Chains: Aatrox fires a demonic chain in a line, damaging and <#ffb900ff>slowing<> enemy champions hit. After a short delay the chain snaps back, dealing damage again and briefly locking enemies caught in the path.",
        "ult": "R - World Ender: Aatrox reveals his demonic form for <#ffb900ff>10.0s<>, gaining <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>75 attack damage<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:speed_0><#ffffffff>20% movement speed<> and <#6aff55ff>50% vamp<>. Nearby enemies are briefly feared on cast."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_viktor": {
        "name": "Viktor",
        "attack": "Arcane Pulse: Viktor fires an arcane bolt, dealing <#a974ffff>12<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> as magic damage. While Siphon Empower is active, his next basic attack deals <#a974ffff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>115% magic power<> and grants Viktor a shield.",
        "skill": "E - Hextech Ray: Viktor's third arm fires a laser in the target direction, dealing magic damage to enemies in a line. When evolved, the ray leaves an aftershock that detonates shortly after, damaging and briefly slowing enemies. Hitting an enemy champion advances Glorious Evolution.",
        "skill2": "Q/W - Siphon Power + Gravity Field: Viktor shields himself and empowers his next basic attack, then creates a gravity field at the target location. Enemies inside are slowed; enemies still in the field when it collapses are stunned. When evolved, the field also disrupts movement skills.",
        "ult": "R - Arcane Storm: Viktor summons an arcane storm at the target location, dealing an initial burst of magic damage and disrupting enemy skills. The storm then pulses repeatedly. Casting Arcane Storm advances Glorious Evolution; once fully evolved, the storm is larger, lasts longer, and pulses faster."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_veigar": {
        "name": "Veigar",
        "attack": "Tire un projectile magique sur une cible, infligeant <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% des dégâts d'attaque<> en <#ff9028ff>dégâts physiques<>.",
        "skill": "Fait tomber de la matière noire sur une zone ciblée après un court délai, infligeant <#a974ffff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>180% AP<> <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<> dans un <#ffb900ff>rayon de 35<>. Toucher un champion ennemi confère <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>22 AP jusqu'à la mort<>; les sbires subissent la moitié des dégâts.",
        "skill2": "Crée une cage d'Horizon des événements. Après <#ffb900ff>1.0s<>, les champions ennemis à l'intérieur sont <#ef5350ff>étourdis pendant 1.5s<> puis la cage disparaît.",
        "ult": "Projette une salve de magie noire sur un champion ennemi, infligeant <#a974ffff>150<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>200% AP<> <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<>."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_jhin": {
        "name": "Jhin",
        "attack": "Tire sur la cible, infligeant <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% des dégâts d'attaque<> en <#ff9028ff>dégâts physiques<>. Chaque quatrième attaque utilise un projectile rouge et inflige <#ff9028ff>100<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>200% des dégâts d'attaque<>. Après le quatrième tir, Jhin recharge avec une vitesse d'attaque fortement réduite jusqu'à sa prochaine attaque.",
        "skill": "Grenade dansante : lance une grenade rebondissante sur un ennemi à portée. La grenade peut sauter vers un autre ennemi proche et inflige <#ff9028ff>40<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>75% des dégâts d'attaque<> en <#ff9028ff>dégâts physiques<> à l'impact.",
        "skill2": "Floraison mortelle : tire une longue ligne, infligeant <#ff9028ff>70<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>70% des dégâts d'attaque<> en <#ff9028ff>dégâts physiques<> aux champions ennemis et <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>30% des dégâts d'attaque<> aux sbires. Les champions ennemis touchés sont <#ef5350ff>étourdis pendant 0.5s<>.",
        "ult": "Rappel de rideau : immobilise Jhin sur place et tire quatre balles ne touchant que les champions dans la direction choisie. Chaque balle s'arrête au premier champion ennemi touché. Les trois premiers tirs infligent <#ff9028ff>300<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>150% des dégâts d'attaque<> en <#ff9028ff>dégâts physiques<>; le quatrième tir rouge, plus grand, inflige <#ff9028ff>300<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>300% des dégâts d'attaque<>."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_vayne": {
        "name": "Vayne",
        "attack": "Tire un carreau d'arbalète sur la cible, infligeant <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% des dégâts d'attaque<> en <#ff9028ff>dégâts physiques<>. Chaque troisième attaque de base déclenche Carreaux d'argent, infligeant <#f5f5f5ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>35% des dégâts d'attaque<> + <#f5f5f5ff>4% des PV max de la cible<> en <#f5f5f5ff>dégâts fixes<>.",
        "skill": "Roulade : roule sur une courte distance dans la direction choisie et renforce la prochaine attaque de base pour infliger <#ff9028ff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>150% des dégâts d'attaque<>. Pendant Combat ultime, Roulade va plus loin et rend Vayne <#ffb900ff>invisible pendant 1.5s<>.",
        "skill2": "Carreaux d'argent : passif, disponible au niveau 1 et toujours actif. Chaque troisième attaque de base inflige des <#f5f5f5ff>dégâts fixes<> supplémentaires.",
        "ult": "Combat ultime : pendant <#ffb900ff>10.0s<>, Vayne gagne <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>50 dégâts d'attaque<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:speed_0><#ffffffff>20% vitesse de déplacement<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:attack_speed_0><#ceff99ff>20% vitesse d'attaque<> et une récupération de compétence plus rapide. Tant que l'effet est actif, Roulade confère l'invisibilité."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_fiddlesticks": {
        "name": "Fiddlesticks",
        "attack": "Lance un projectile en forme de corbeau sur la cible, infligeant <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% AP<> en <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<>.",
        "skill": "Terreur : envoie un projectile cauchemardesque sur un champion ennemi, infligeant <#a974ffff>45<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>70% AP<> <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<> et l'effrayant pendant 1.25 seconde.",
        "skill2": "Moisson fructueuse : draine brièvement les ennemis proches, infligeant plusieurs fois <#a974ffff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>25% AP<> <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<> et soignant Fiddlesticks de <#6aff55ff>30<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#6aff55ff>8% AP<> par ennemi touché.",
        "ult": "Rafale de corbeaux : se téléporte sur un champion ennemi, effraie brièvement les champions ennemis proches et entoure Fiddlesticks d'une tempête pendant 2 secondes, infligeant plusieurs fois <#a974ffff>26<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>30% AP<> <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<> aux ennemis proches."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_azir": {
        "name": "Azir",
        "attack": "Azir dirige la magie du sable vers la cible, infligeant 75% AP dégâts magiques et faisant parfois apparaître des soldats de sable pour rejoindre le combat.",
        "skill": "Dresse-toi ! : envoie un soldat de sable vers une zone ciblée, infligeant 30 + 60% AP dégâts magiques aux ennemis traversés. À l'arrivée, le soldat reste sur place et attaque les ennemis proches, infligeant 15 + 70% AP dégâts magiques par frappe aux champions.",
        "skill2": "Sables mouvants : invoque un soldat de sable et fonce vers lui, gagnant un bouclier de 70 + 45% AP. Les ennemis traversés par Azir subissent 40 + 45% AP dégâts magiques. Le soldat reste après la ruée.",
        "ult": "Partition impériale : envoie un mur de soldats vers l'avant, infligeant 120 + 100% AP dégâts magiques aux ennemis sur sa trajectoire, les repoussant et les projetant brièvement dans les airs. Le mur reste un court instant et gêne les déplacements à travers lui."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_fizz": {
        "name": "Fizz",
        "attack": "Frappe la cible au corps à corps, infligeant <#a974ffff>10<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>100% AP<> <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<>. Après Frappe de l'oursin, les attaques de base appliquent brièvement du poison à l'impact.",
        "skill": "Frappe de l'oursin : traverse la cible et atterrit derrière elle, infligeant <#a974ffff>40<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>55% AP<> <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<> et l'empoisonnant pendant <#ffb900ff>3.0s<>. Pendant <#ffb900ff>4.0s<> après l'impact, les attaques de base de Fizz appliquent un poison plus léger à l'impact.",
        "skill2": "Joueur / Filou : bondit vers une direction ennemie ou alliée choisie, reste brièvement sur sa perche en étant <#ffb900ff>invisible, avec dégâts réduits et immunité aux contrôles pendant 2.4s<>, puis redescend sur une courte distance et éclabousse la zone pour infliger <#a974ffff>70<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>65% AP<> <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<> et <#ef5350ff>ralentir les ennemis proches pendant 0.5s<>.",
        "ult": "Pêche au gros : lance un poisson à longue portée dans la direction choisie. Le poisson s'arrête sur le premier champion ennemi touché et le <#ef5350ff>ralentit fortement pendant 2.5s<>; s'il rate, il atteint la fin de sa trajectoire. Un requin apparaît pendant le ralentissement, puis surgit pour infliger <#a974ffff>240<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>140% AP<> <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<> et <#ef5350ff>projeter les ennemis dans les airs<>."
      },
      "bo_league_champions_ezreal": {
        "name": "Ezreal",
        "attack": "Tire un projectile énergétique sur la cible, infligeant <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>100% des dégâts d’attaque<> en <#ff9028ff>dégâts physiques<>.",
        "skill": "Tir mystique : tire un projectile rapide dans la direction choisie, s’arrêtant au premier ennemi touché et infligeant <#ff9028ff>50<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% des dégâts d’attaque<> en <#ff9028ff>dégâts physiques<> aux champions. Les sbires subissent la moitié des dégâts.",
        "skill2": "Transfert arcanique : se téléporte sur une courte distance dans la direction choisie.",
        "ult": "Barrage térébrant : tire une attaque à portée illimitée vers les ennemis, infligeant <#ff9028ff>220<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>110% des dégâts d’attaque<> en <#ff9028ff>dégâts physiques<>, plus <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>70% AP<> en <#a974ffff>dégâts magiques<> aux ennemis touchés."
      },
      "test_mod_aatrox": {
        "name": "Aatrox",
        "attack": "Deathbringer Stance: empowers the next greatsword strike, dealing <#ff9028ff>18<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>112% attack damage<> as <#ff9028ff>physical damage<>.",
        "skill": "Q - The Darkin Blade: each cast releases one strike of Aatrox's three-part blade combo. Q1 is a narrow thrust, Q2 is a wide cleave, and Q3 is a heavy smash that hits hardest and <#ef5350ff>knocks enemies airborne for 0.5s<>. Casting Q again advances to the next strike instead of firing all three at once.",
        "skill2": "W - Infernal Chains: Aatrox fires a demonic chain in a line, damaging and <#ffb900ff>slowing<> enemy champions hit. After a short delay the chain snaps back, dealing damage again and briefly locking enemies caught in the path.",
        "ult": "R - World Ender: Aatrox reveals his demonic form for <#ffb900ff>10.0s<>, gaining <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ad_0><#ff9028ff>75 attack damage<>, <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:speed_0><#ffffffff>20% movement speed<> and <#6aff55ff>50% vamp<>. Nearby enemies are briefly feared on cast."
      },
      "test_mod_viktor": {
        "name": "Viktor",
        "attack": "Arcane Pulse: Viktor fires an arcane bolt, dealing <#a974ffff>12<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>75% magic power<> as magic damage. While Siphon Empower is active, his next basic attack deals <#a974ffff>35<> + <i#asset/base/ui/banpick/champion_stat_icon:ap_0><#a974ffff>115% magic power<> and grants Viktor a shield.",
        "skill": "E - Hextech Ray: Viktor's third arm fires a laser in the target direction, dealing magic damage to enemies in a line. When evolved, the ray leaves an aftershock that detonates shortly after, damaging and briefly slowing enemies. Hitting an enemy champion advances Glorious Evolution.",
        "skill2": "Q/W - Siphon Power + Gravity Field: Viktor shields himself and empowers his next basic attack, then creates a gravity field at the target location. Enemies inside are slowed; enemies still in the field when it collapses are stunned. When evolved, the field also disrupts movement skills.",
        "ult": "R - Arcane Storm: Viktor summons an arcane storm at the target location, dealing an initial burst of magic damage and disrupting enemy skills. The storm then pulses repeatedly. Casting Arcane Storm advances Glorious Evolution; once fully evolved, the storm is larger, lasts longer, and pulses faster."
      },
